{"tid":1443633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再活動多到俾人揀今日去邊！","createTime":"2019-08-11T09:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T10:55:14.000Z","uid":280724,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bb578db59871f815016e4cbe11f2f052e8ecd80b","tid":1443633,"uid":280724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"一日最多只可以有兩場活動<br />\n<br />\n一場係老少咸宜嘅終極和理非<br />\n一場係有機會勇武上場嘅街頭抗爭<br />\n<br />\n人手唔重疊，用盡所有唔同屬性嘅人，唔同嘅人手唔可以有得揀，只有一個活動，勇武上場後地點再自由發揮<br />\n勇武果日攰嘅可以去和理非休息<br />\n<br />\n活動搞手如發現同日有重疊，適宜主動溝通，除非地點係一南一北，否則適宜改期<br />\n<br />\n咁玩落去人數唔夠會玩死自己<br />\n<br />\n唔好再俾我揀喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692ea2806dfdbdf5073d2640deffb0b1a52588ef","tid":1443633,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"【戰略】撳美金現金係最低成本嘅革命手段，成功嘅話無需攬炒，得中共自炒。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/adjxyOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/adjxyOU</a>"},{"pid":"25d8633770eee8c068722634463fe9670216dc92","tid":1443633,"uid":280724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:21:13.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"89e4d1246b51850d9fc31ff645f8d5d3ed3e13dc","tid":1443633,"uid":280724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"02bd0f35acaf7860193ffa5fc7dced51412b4fe8","tid":1443633,"uid":280724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:21:33.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"8b5c3d3e6a9fc693df355c896b5932880fab8641","tid":1443633,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:22:00.000Z","msg":"講得岩"},{"pid":"64688364b75849eddee4b24164345538a314d5af","tid":1443633,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:22:47.000Z","msg":"agger, 今日唔知想點"},{"pid":"8c9408cdcbcd344baf4745708ebfaf06dc6edeec","tid":1443633,"uid":134924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":